Shrimp Garlic Cream Soup

30 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

shellfishdairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freelow-carb

Cuisine:

AmericanSeafood

Course:

SoupMain Dish

Tags:

soupseafoodcreamyeasy

Description

A creamy and savory soup that combines the rich flavors of shrimp and garlic, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • shrimp: 1 pound (peeled and deveined)
  • garlic: 4 cloves (minced)
  • onion: 1 medium (chopped)
  • chicken broth: 4 cups
  • heavy cream: 1 cup
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
